   MONICA-TV-REVIEW _ It has been a They-Shoot-Lawyers-Don't-They?
marathon for viewers of the legal analysts who fog up the TV
screens with talk about the Monica S. Lewinsky investigation. By
Jill Abramson. WITH GRAPHIC.  &QL;
